name: Oda Non Style LORA
description:
This is my second attempt on Oda Non's style. I like how it worked out.

Hope you guys like it too.

All the images were generated using the LORA at 0.55 - 0.60 weight
Trained over AbyssOrangeMix 2 Hard

320 x 320 Highres x2 Latent DMP++ 2M Karras at around 0.6 denoise

Special thanks to @ThunderboltRED for the dataset and idea :D
